---
import TVLayout from '../layouts/TVLayout.astro'
---

<TVLayout>
  <article class="bio">
    <p class="big-text">
      Hi! I'm <span class="bio__photo" tabindex="0">Christian Kaisermann</span>,
      a
      <button class="button-text js-channel-trigger" data-channel="8"
        >Carioca</button
      >
      based in Berlin, web engineer, CSS enthusiast and avid open-sourcerer.
      <br /><br />Currently, I'm focused on improving the last-mile delivery
      experience for
      <a
        href="https://www.getcircuit.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Circuit Routing</a
      >.
      <br /><br />I'm a very outgoing and curious person, who's passionate about
      <a
        href="https://github.com/kaisermann"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">coding</a
      >, photography, nature, cats, and music. I love to stare at a
      <a
        href="https://justgetflux.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">not-so-bright screen</a
      >
      while coding on a constant state of
      <a
        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flow_(psychology)"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Flow</a
      >. Here are some <a href="/playlists">playlists</a> to get you going.
      <br /><br />If you'd like to chat, feel free to reach me by
      <a href="mailto:christian@kaisermann.me">e-mail</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</TVLayout>

<style>
  .bio__photo {
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-secondary);

    &::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      position: absolute;
      z-index: var(--layer-me-hover);
      top: calc(100% + 1em);
      left: 1rem;
      width: 14rem;
      padding-bottom: 14rem;
      visibility: hidden;
      background-size: cover;
    }

    &:hover::after,
    &:focus::after {
      background-image: url(/assets/images/me.jpg);
      transition: visibility 0s 0.2s;
      visibility: visible;
    }
  }
</style>
